<section class="slide" data-title="Why this works">
  <div class="kicker">Why this works</div>
  <h2>Music-making is for everyone now</h2>
  <p class="lead">This workflow breaks songwriting into bite-sized, logical milestones. AI acts as an empowering creative companion — it helps with sequencing, vocabulary retrieval (an advanced thesaurus), and audio production.</p>
