<!-- ============ SLIDE 5 : PHASE 2 ============ -->
<section class="slide" data-title="Phase 2">
  <span class="phase-badge">Phase 2 · AI Lyric Construction</span>
  <h2>The Thesaurus Method</h2>
  <h3>1 · Structural framework</h3>
  <p>Map your story into song components — alternating verses, a repetitive chorus, maybe a bridge.</p>
  <h3>2 · AI vocabulary support</h3>
  <p>Feed your prose to an AI tool. Ask for <strong>rhyming pairs, rhythmic phrases, and emotional synonyms</strong> that fit your melody — while keeping your original voice.</p>
  <div class="note">
    <span class="tag">Troy says</span>
    <p>"With AI, I narrow it down and I use AI like a thesaurus. Sometimes I pick words from my original story to complement the rhyming and the melody."</p>
  </div>
</section>

